summary: This is wnisewond's true final contribution to nexus. Please enjoy this mod as wnisewond will no be making any more presets.
descriptionHtml:
[size=5]This is the final release of wnisewond's presets converted into followers. Wnisewond has agreed to let me do his select presets. 

[/size][size=4]Amelia Rose 

weight: 0.25 
body: UUNP Dangerously THICC
voice type: female young eager
Level: 30-150
As usual like all of my other followers, she is marriageable and essential.
Combat Style: All of the attributes required by a Storm Mage.
Outfit: Dragons Crown Sorceress
